<eesti> Et uue &uuml;ldkasutatava telefoniteenuse loomine eeldab kuudepikkust ettevalmistust, on k&otilde;nealuse 11 kuu pikkuse lisarakendusajaga t&otilde;en&auml;olistele investoritele tekitatav v&otilde;imalik kahju piiratud j&auml;rgmistel p&otilde;hjustel: a) k&otilde;nealused investorid v&otilde;ivad juba n&uuml;&uuml;d kavandada oma investeeringuid ja b) ametlikud litsentsimistingimused avaldatakse hiljemalt 1. augustil 1998. </eesti>
<inglise> That will mean that new entrants will be ready to be operational in advance of full liberalization. </inglise>
<eesti> See t&auml;hendab, et uued turuletulijad on valmis tegevust alustama enne t&auml;ielikku liberaliseerimist. </eesti>
<inglise> In addition, the effective liberalization of the market will be more rapidly achieved to the benefit of new market entrants given that the access conditions will in the meantime be settled between Telefonica and the initial competitors. </inglise>
<eesti> Lisaks sellele toimub turu tulemuslik liberaliseerimine kiiremini ja sellest on kasu ka uutel turuletulijatel, v&otilde;ttes arvesse, et enne seda otsustavad Telef&oacute;nica ja esimesed konkurendid turulep&auml;&auml;su tingimused. </eesti>
<inglise> Finally, no additional implementation period with regard to any other market segment has been requested by the Spanish authorities. </inglise>
<eesti> Hispaania ametiasutused ei ole taotlenud lisarakendusaega &uuml;hegi teise turuosa puhul. </eesti>
<inglise> On the basis that the publication of licences will take place no later than 1 August 1998, and mindful of Article 9 (2) of Directive 97/13/EC of the European Parliament and the Council of 10 April 1997 on a common framework for general authorizations and individual licences in the field of telecommunications services (14), the Spanish authorities have stated that they will grant licences for the provision of public fixed voice telephony within four months of publication, to those undertakings which submit licence applications in good time. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui litsentside avaldamine toimub hiljemalt 1. augustil 1998 ning v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Parlamendi ja n&otilde;ukogu 10. aprilli 1997. aasta direktiivi 97/13/E&Uuml; (telekommunikatsiooniteenuste valdkonna &uuml;ldlubade ja individuaalsete litsentside &uuml;hise raamistiku kohta) (14) artikli 9 l&otilde;iget 2, on Hispaania ametiasutused v&auml;itnud, et nad annavad &uuml;ldkasutatava tavatelefoniv&otilde;rgu k&otilde;neteenuse litsentsid v&auml;lja nelja kuu jooksul p&auml;rast avaldamist neile ettev&otilde;tjatele, kes esitavad oma litsentsitaotluse &otilde;igeks ajaks. </eesti>
<inglise> This will coincide with the completion of the implementation of the new numbering plan and will achieve the full liberalization of the voice-telephony and public telecommunications networks market in Spain. </inglise>
<eesti> See langeb kokku uue numeratsiooniplaani rakendamise l&otilde;petamisega ja aitab kaasa Hispaania k&otilde;neside ja &uuml;ldkasutatavate telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rkude turu t&auml;ielikule liberaliseerimisele. </eesti>
<inglise> (20) The Commission moreover takes note that the new numbering plan has already been decided and that Spain will only spread over time the completion of its full implementation and will respect its obligations under Article 3b of Directive 90/388/EEC. </inglise>
<eesti> 20) Samuti juhib komisjon t&auml;helepanu sellele, et otsus uue numeratsiooniplaani kohta on juba tehtud ning Hispaania tegeleb selle t&auml;ieliku rakendamise l&otilde;petamisega pikema aja jooksul ja peab kinni oma kohustustest, mis tulenevad direktiivi 90/388/EM&Uuml; artiklist 3b. </eesti>
<inglise> Sufficient numbers will be granted already before that date to Retevision, to the new operator to be licensed in early January, to the cable TV companies and to providers of services other than voice telephony. </inglise>
<eesti> Juba enne k&otilde;nealust kuup&auml;eva antakse piisav hulk numbreid Retevisi&oacute;nile, jaanuari alguses litsentsi saavale uuele operaatorile, kaabeltelevisiooniettev&otilde;tjatele ja muude teenuste kui k&otilde;nesideteenuste osutajatele. </eesti>
<inglise> Conclusion </inglise>
<eesti> J&auml;reldus </eesti>
<inglise> (21) On the basis of the above assessment, the Commission considers that the development of trade which would result from the granting to Spain of the following additional implementation periods under Article 2 (2) of Directive 90/388/EEC will not be affected to such an extent as to be contrary to the interests of the Community, in so far as the circumstances set out above are fulfilled: </inglise>
<eesti> 21) Eespool esitatud hinnangu p&otilde;hjal leiab komisjon, et kui Hispaaniale antakse j&auml;rgmised lisarakendusajad vastavalt direktiivi 90/388/EM&Uuml; artikli 2 l&otilde;ikele 2, siis ei m&otilde;jutata see kaubanduse arengut sellises ulatuses, et see oleks vastuolus &uuml;henduse huvidega, kui eespool s&auml;testatud tingimused on t&auml;idetud: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) until 1 January 1998 instead of 1 January 1997 as regards the notification to the Commission of licensing or declaration procedures for the provision of voice telephony and the establishment of public telecommunications networks, and of the details of the national scheme envisaged to share the net cost of the provision of the USO; </inglise>
<eesti> a) 1. jaanuarini 1998, mitte 1. jaanuarini 1997, selleks et teatada komisjonile k&otilde;nesideteenuse osutamise ja &uuml;ldkasutatavate telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rkude loomise litsentsimis- v&otilde;i deklareerimiskorrast ja universaalteenuse osutamise kohustuse netokulutuste jagamiseks kavandatud riikliku kava &uuml;ksikasjadest; </eesti>
<inglise> and (b) until 1 August 1998 instead of 1 July 1997 as regards the publication of licensing or declaration procedures for the provision of voice telephony and public telecommunications networks, including details of the national scheme envisaged to share the net cost of the provision of the USO; </inglise>
<eesti> b) 1. augustini 1998, mitte 1. juulini 1997, selleks et avaldada k&otilde;nesideteenuse osutamise ja &uuml;ldkasutatavate telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rkude loomise litsentsimis- v&otilde;i deklareerimiskord, sealhulgas universaalteenuse osutamise kohustuse netokulutuste jagamiseks kavandatud riikliku kava &uuml;ksikasjad; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) as a consequence of those two extensions, and in accordance with the deadlines set out in Article 9 (2) of Directive 97/13/EC, further licences for the provision of voice telephony and public telecommunications networks (in addition to those mentioned in paragraph 7 of this Decision) will only be granted as from 1 December 1998, </inglise>
<eesti> c) nende kahe pikenduse tagaj&auml;rjel ja koosk&otilde;las direktiivi 97/13/E&Uuml; artikli 9 l&otilde;ikes 2 etten&auml;htud t&auml;htaegadega antakse t&auml;iendavaid k&otilde;nesideteenuse osutamise ja &uuml;ldkasutatava telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu loomise litsentse (lisaks neile, mida on nimetatud k&auml;esoleva otsuse l&otilde;ikes 7) alles alates 1. detsembrist 1998, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS DECISION: </inglise>
